trpzInfoRFDetectMib.name: trpzInfoRFDetectMib

revisions.description: v1.3.1: Added one table: trpzInfoRFDetectClientTable to support detected Clients and RFID tags (for 7.7 release).
v1.2.0: Added one scalar: trpzInfoRFDetectCurrentXmtrTableSize (for 6.2 release)
v1.1.0: Added three new columnar objects: - trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrNetworkingMode, - trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrClassification, - trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrClassificationReason (for 6.2 release)

trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrTable.name: trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrTable
trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrTable.description: Transmitter table. May contain tens of thousands of entries (different Transmitter-Listener-Channel combinations).

trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrTransmitterMacAddres.name: trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrTransmitterMacAddress
trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrTransmitterMacAddres.description: The MAC Address of this Transmitter.

trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrListenerMacAddress.name: trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrListenerMacAddress
trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrListenerMacAddress.description: The MAC Address of this Listener.

trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrChannelNum.name: trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrChannelNum
trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrChannelNum.description: Channel Number this transmitter was using when this listener detected it.

trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrRssi.name: trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrRssi
trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrRssi.description: Received Signal Strength Indicator at this listener.

trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrSsid.name: trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrSsid
trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrSsid.description: The service/SSID name this transmitter was using. Zero-length string when unknown or not applicable.

trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrNetworkingMode.name: trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrNetworkingMode
trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrNetworkingMode.description: The way this transmitter is doing wireless networking: ad-hoc mode networking or infrastructure mode networking.

trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrClassification.name: trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrClassification
trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrClassification.description: The RF classification of this transmitter.

trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrClassificationReason.name: trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrClassificationReason
trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrClassificationReason.description: The reason why this transmitter was classified by RF detection the way it is.

trpzInfoRFDetectClientTable.name: trpzInfoRFDetectClientTable
trpzInfoRFDetectClientTable.description: Client table, including RFID tags. Contains Client-Listener combinations.

trpzInfoRFDetectClientEntry.name: trpzInfoRFDetectClientEntry
trpzInfoRFDetectClientEntry.description: Information about a particular Client, as it was detected by a particular listener (AP radio).

trpzInfoRFDetectClientMacAddress.name: trpzInfoRFDetectClientMacAddress
trpzInfoRFDetectClientMacAddress.description: The MAC Address of this Client.

trpzInfoRFDetectClientListenerMacAddress.name: trpzInfoRFDetectClientListenerMacAddress
trpzInfoRFDetectClientListenerMacAddress.description: The MAC Address of this Listener (AP radio).

trpzInfoRFDetectClientConnectedBssid.name: trpzInfoRFDetectClientConnectedBssid
trpzInfoRFDetectClientConnectedBssid.description: The service MAC address (a.k.a. BSSID) this Client was Connected to when last detected by this listener. If this information is not available, the value will be 0:0:0:0:0:0.

trpzInfoRFDetectClientApNum.name: trpzInfoRFDetectClientApNum
trpzInfoRFDetectClientApNum.description: Number of the AP (listener) that detected this Client.

trpzInfoRFDetectClientApRadioIndex.name: trpzInfoRFDetectClientApRadioIndex
trpzInfoRFDetectClientApRadioIndex.description: Number of the AP Radio (listener) that detected this Client.

trpzInfoRFDetectClientModulation.name: trpzInfoRFDetectClientModulation
trpzInfoRFDetectClientModulation.description: 802.11 Modulation standard this Client was using when last detected by this listener (a, b, g, n/a, n/g).

trpzInfoRFDetectClientChannelNum.name: trpzInfoRFDetectClientChannelNum
trpzInfoRFDetectClientChannelNum.description: Channel Number this Client was using when last detected by this listener.

trpzInfoRFDetectClientRate.name: trpzInfoRFDetectClientRate
trpzInfoRFDetectClientRate.description: Packet data rate this Client was using when last detected by this listener.

trpzInfoRFDetectClientRssi.name: trpzInfoRFDetectClientRssi
trpzInfoRFDetectClientRssi.description: Received Signal Strength Indicator for this Client when last detected by this listener.

trpzInfoRFDetectClientClassification.name: trpzInfoRFDetectClientClassification
trpzInfoRFDetectClientClassification.description: The RF classification of this Client.

trpzInfoRFDetectCurrentXmtrTableSize.name: trpzInfoRFDetectCurrentXmtrTableSize
trpzInfoRFDetectCurrentXmtrTableSize.description: Current number of Transmitter-Listener-Channel combinations found and recorded by RF detection.

trpzInfoRFDetectCompliance.name: trpzInfoRFDetectCompliance
trpzInfoRFDetectCompliance.description: The compliance statement for devices that implement the RF Detect MIB. This compliance statement is for releases 6.0 to 7.6 of AC (wireless switch) software.

trpzInfoRFDetectComplianceRev2.name: trpzInfoRFDetectComplianceRev2
trpzInfoRFDetectComplianceRev2.description: The compliance statement for devices that implement the RF Detect MIB. This compliance statement is for releases 7.7 and greater of AC (wireless switch) software.

trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrGroup.name: trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrGroup
trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrGroup.description: Mandatory group of objects implemented to provide RF Detect Transmitter info.

trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrClassificationGroup.name: trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrClassificationGroup
trpzInfoRFDetectXmtrClassificationGroup.description: Group of objects implemented to provide RF Detect Classification info. Introduced in 6.2 release.

trpzInfoRFDetectCurrentXmtrTableSizeGrou.name: trpzInfoRFDetectCurrentXmtrTableSizeGroup
trpzInfoRFDetectCurrentXmtrTableSizeGrou.description: Group for one object that provides the current number of Transmitter-Listener-Channel combinations found and recorded by RF detection. Introduced in 6.2 release.

trpzInfoRFDetectClientGroup.name: trpzInfoRFDetectClientGroup
trpzInfoRFDetectClientGroup.description: Mandatory group of objects implemented to provide RF Detect Client info in releases 7.7 and greater.
